had a chance to notice,

04:55.586 --> 04:59.421
but she has gum in her hair...
again.

04:59.423 --> 05:01.258
I think she's being bullied
at school.

05:03.261 --> 05:05.385
I think you need
to talk to her.

05:05.387 --> 05:07.262
Okay, okay.
I'm on it.

05:07.264 --> 05:08.389
- Okay.
- All right.

05:08.391 --> 05:09.598
All right.

05:09.600 --> 05:10.724
I gotta go back.

05:10.726 --> 05:11.851
Okay. I'll see you tomorrow.

05:11.853 --> 05:12.685
- Bye.
- Bye.

05:12.687 --> 05:13.519
See you.

05:13.521 --> 05:15.562
